3657 if (model->nummaterial && !(flags & M3D_EXP_NOMATERIAL)) {
3658 for (j = 0; j < model->nummaterial; j++) {
3659 if (mtrlidx[j] == M3D_UNDEF || !model->material[j].numprop || !model->material[j].prop) continue;
3660 m = &model->material[j];
3661 sn = _m3d_safestr(m->name, 0);
3662 if (!sn) {
3663 setlocale(LC_NUMERIC, ol);

3668 for (i = 0; i < m->numprop; i++) {
3669 if (m->prop[i].type < 128)
3670 len += 32;
3671 else if (m->prop[i].value.textureid < model->numtexture && model->texture[m->prop[i].value.textureid].name)
3672 len += (unsigned int)strlen(model->texture[m->prop[i].value.textureid].name) + 16;

3682 sn = NULL;

3684 k = 256;
3685 if (m->prop[i].type >= 128) {

3687 if (m->prop[i].type == m3d_propertytypes[l].id) {

3700 if (m->prop[i].type == m3d_propertytypes[l].id) {

3708 case m3dpf_uint8:
3709 case m3dpf_uint16:
3710 case m3dpf_uint32: ptr += sprintf(ptr, "%s %d\r\n", sn, m->prop[i].value.num); break;
3711 case m3dpf_float: ptr += sprintf(ptr, "%s %g\r\n", sn, m->prop[i].value.fnum); break;

3733 /* procedural face */
3734 if (model->numinlined && model->inlined && !(flags & M3D_EXP_NOFACE)) {
3735 /* all inlined assets which are not textures should be procedural surfaces */
3736 for (j = 0; j < model->numinlined; j++) {
3737 if (!model->inlined[j].name || !*model->inlined[j].name || !model->inlined[j].length || !model->inlined[j].data ||
3738 (model->inlined[j].data[1] == 'P' && model->inlined[j].data[2] == 'N' && model->inlined[j].data[3] == 'G'))
3739 continue;
3740 for (i = k = 0; i < model->numtexture; i++) {
3741 if (!strcmp(model->inlined[j].name, model->texture[i].name)) {
3742 k = 1;
3743 break;
3744 }

3746 if (k) continue;
3747 sn = _m3d_safestr(model->inlined[j].name, 0);
3748 if (!sn) {

3765 /* mesh face */
3766 if (model->numface && face && !(flags & M3D_EXP_NOFACE)) {

3769 last = M3D_UNDEF;
3770 if (!(flags & M3D_EXP_NOMATERIAL))

3773 if (j != last) {
3774 last = j;
3775 if (last < model->nummaterial)
3776 len += (unsigned int)strlen(model->material[last].name);
3777 len += 6;

3780 out = (unsigned char *)M3D_REALLOC(out, len);
3781 ptr += (uintptr_t)out;
3782 if (!out) {
3783 setlocale(LC_NUMERIC, ol);
3784 goto memerr;
3785 }
3786 ptr += sprintf(ptr, "Mesh\r\n");
3787 last = M3D_UNDEF;
3788 for (i = 0; i < model->numface; i++) {
3789 j = face[i].data.materialid < model->nummaterial ? face[i].data.materialid : M3D_UNDEF;
3790 if (!(flags & M3D_EXP_NOMATERIAL) && j != last) {
3791 last = j;
3792 if (last < model->nummaterial) {
3793 sn = _m3d_safestr(model->material[last].name, 0);
3794 if (!sn) {
3795 setlocale(LC_NUMERIC, ol);
3796 goto memerr;
3797 }
3798 ptr += sprintf(ptr, "use %s\r\n", sn);
3799 M3D_FREE(sn);
3800 sn = NULL;
3801 } else
3802 ptr += sprintf(ptr, "use\r\n");
3803 }
3804 /* hardcoded triangles. Should be repeated as many times as the number of edges in polygon */
3805 for (j = 0; j < 3; j++) {
3806 ptr += sprintf(ptr, "%s%d", j ? " " : "", vrtxidx[face[i].data.vertex[j]]);
3807 k = M3D_NOTDEFINED;
3808 if (!(flags & M3D_EXP_NOTXTCRD) && (face[i].data.texcoord[j] != M3D_UNDEF) &&
3809 (tmapidx[face[i].data.texcoord[j]] != M3D_UNDEF)) {
3810 k = tmapidx[face[i].data.texcoord[j]];
3811 ptr += sprintf(ptr, "/%d", k);

4275 }

4277 *length = (uint32_t)((uintptr_t)out - (uintptr_t)((uint8_t *)h + len));
4278 out = NULL;
4279 len += *length;
4280 }
4281 /* materials */
4282 if (model->nummaterial && !(flags & M3D_EXP_NOMATERIAL)) {
4283 for (j = 0; j < model->nummaterial; j++) {
4284 if (mtrlidx[j] == M3D_UNDEF || !model->material[j].numprop || !model->material[j].prop) continue;
4285 m = &model->material[j];
4286 chunklen = 12 + si_s + m->numprop * 5;
4287 h = (m3dhdr_t *)M3D_REALLOC(h, len + chunklen);
4288 if (!h) goto memerr;
4289 memcpy((uint8_t *)h + len, "MTRL", 4);
4290 length = (uint32_t *)((uint8_t *)h + len + 4);
4291 out = (uint8_t *)h + len + 8;
4292 out = _m3d_addidx(out, si_s, _m3d_stridx(str, numstr, m->name));
4293 for (i = 0; i < m->numprop; i++) {
4294 if (m->prop[i].type >= 128) {
4295 if (m->prop[i].value.textureid >= model->numtexture ||
4296 !model->texture[m->prop[i].value.textureid].name) continue;
4297 k = m3dpf_map;
4298 } else {
4299 for (k = 256, l = 0; l < sizeof(m3d_propertytypes) / sizeof(m3d_propertytypes[0]); l++)
4300 if (m->prop[i].type == m3d_propertytypes[l].id) {
4301 k = m3d_propertytypes[l].format;
4302 break;
4303 }
4304 }
4305 if (k == 256) continue;
4306 *out++ = m->prop[i].type;
4307 switch (k) {
4308 case m3dpf_color:
4309 if (!(flags & M3D_EXP_NOCMAP)) {
4310 idx = _m3d_cmapidx(cmap, numcmap, m->prop[i].value.color);
4311 switch (ci_s) {
4312 case 1: *out++ = (uint8_t)(idx); break;
4313 case 2:
4314 *((uint16_t *)out) = (uint16_t)(idx);
4315 out += 2;
4316 break;
4317 case 4:
4318 *((uint32_t *)out) = (uint32_t)(m->prop[i].value.color);
4319 out += 4;
4320 break;
4321 }
4322 } else
4323 out--;
4324 break;
4325 case m3dpf_uint8: *out++ = (uint8_t)m->prop[i].value.num; break;
4326 case m3dpf_uint16:
4327 *((uint16_t *)out) = (uint16_t)m->prop[i].value.num;
4328 out += 2;
4329 break;
4330 case m3dpf_uint32:
4331 *((uint32_t *)out) = m->prop[i].value.num;
4332 out += 4;
4333 break;
4334 case m3dpf_float:
4335 *((float *)out) = m->prop[i].value.fnum;
4336 out += 4;
4337 break;
4338
4339 case m3dpf_map:
4340 idx = _m3d_stridx(str, numstr, model->texture[m->prop[i].value.textureid].name);
4341 out = _m3d_addidx(out, si_s, idx);
4342 break;
4343 }
4344 }
4345 *length = (uint32_t)((uintptr_t)out - (uintptr_t)((uint8_t *)h + len));
4346 len += *length;
4347 out = NULL;
4348 }
4349 }
4350 /* procedural face */
4351 if (model->numinlined && model->inlined && !(flags & M3D_EXP_NOFACE)) {
4352 /* all inlined assets which are not textures should be procedural surfaces */
4353 for (j = 0; j < model->numinlined; j++) {
4354 if (!model->inlined[j].name || !model->inlined[j].name[0] || model->inlined[j].length < 4 ||
4355 !model->inlined[j].data || (model->inlined[j].data[1] == 'P' && model->inlined[j].data[2] == 'N' && model->inlined[j].data[3] == 'G'))
4356 continue;
4357 for (i = k = 0; i < model->numtexture; i++) {
4358 if (!strcmp(model->inlined[j].name, model->texture[i].name)) {
4359 k = 1;
4360 break;
4361 }
4362 }
4363 if (k) continue;
4364 numproc++;
4365 chunklen = 8 + si_s;
4366 h = (m3dhdr_t *)M3D_REALLOC(h, len + chunklen);
4367 if (!h) goto memerr;
4368 memcpy((uint8_t *)h + len, "PROC", 4);
4369 *((uint32_t *)((uint8_t *)h + len + 4)) = chunklen;
4370 out = (uint8_t *)h + len + 8;
4371 out = _m3d_addidx(out, si_s, _m3d_stridx(str, numstr, model->inlined[j].name));
4372 out = NULL;
4373 len += chunklen;
4374 }
4375 }
4376 /* mesh face */
4377 if (model->numface && face && !(flags & M3D_EXP_NOFACE)) {
4378 chunklen = 8 + si_s + model->numface * (6 * vi_s + 3 * ti_s + si_s + 1);
4379 h = (m3dhdr_t *)M3D_REALLOC(h, len + chunklen);
4380 if (!h) goto memerr;
4381 memcpy((uint8_t *)h + len, "MESH", 4);
4382 length = (uint32_t *)((uint8_t *)h + len + 4);
4383 out = (uint8_t *)h + len + 8;
4384 last = M3D_UNDEF;
4385 for (i = 0; i < model->numface; i++) {
4386 if (!(flags & M3D_EXP_NOMATERIAL) && face[i].data.materialid != last) {
4387 last = face[i].data.materialid;
4388 idx = last < model->nummaterial ? _m3d_stridx(str, numstr, model->material[last].name) : 0;
4389 *out++ = 0;
4390 out = _m3d_addidx(out, si_s, idx);
4391 }
4392 /* hardcoded triangles. */
4393 k = (3 << 4) |
4394 (((flags & M3D_EXP_NOTXTCRD) || !ti_s || face[i].data.texcoord[0] == M3D_UNDEF ||
4395 face[i].data.texcoord[1] == M3D_UNDEF || face[i].data.texcoord[2] == M3D_UNDEF) ?
4396 0 :
4397 1) |
4398 (((flags & M3D_EXP_NONORMAL) || face[i].data.normal[0] == M3D_UNDEF ||
4399 face[i].data.normal[1] == M3D_UNDEF || face[i].data.normal[2] == M3D_UNDEF) ?
4400 0 :
4401 2);
4402 *out++ = (uint8_t)k;
4403 for (j = 0; j < 3; j++) {
4404 out = _m3d_addidx(out, vi_s, vrtxidx[face[i].data.vertex[j]]);
4405 if (k & 1)
4406 out = _m3d_addidx(out, ti_s, tmapidx[face[i].data.texcoord[j]]);
4407 if (k & 2)
4408 out = _m3d_addidx(out, vi_s, vrtxidx[face[i].data.normal[j]]);
4409 }
4410 }
4411 uint32_t v = (uint32_t)((uintptr_t)out - (uintptr_t)((uint8_t *)h + len));
4412 memcpy(length, &v, sizeof(uint32_t));
4413 len += v;
4414 out = NULL;
4415 }
4416 /* mathematical shapes face */
4417 if (model->numshape && model->shape && !(flags & M3D_EXP_NOFACE)) {
4418 for (j = 0; j < model->numshape; j++) {
4419 chunklen = 12 + si_s + model->shape[j].numcmd * (M3D_CMDMAXARG + 1) * 4;
4420 h = (m3dhdr_t *)M3D_REALLOC(h, len + chunklen);
4421 if (!h) goto memerr;
4422 memcpy((uint8_t *)h + len, "SHPE", 4);
4423 length = (uint32_t *)((uint8_t *)h + len + 4);
4424 out = (uint8_t *)h + len + 8;
4425 out = _m3d_addidx(out, si_s, _m3d_stridx(str, numstr, model->shape[j].name));
4426 out = _m3d_addidx(out, bi_s, model->shape[j].group);
4427 for (i = 0; i < model->shape[j].numcmd; i++) {
4428 cmd = &model->shape[j].cmd[i];
4429 if (cmd->type >= (unsigned int)(sizeof(m3d_commandtypes) / sizeof(m3d_commandtypes[0])) || !cmd->arg)
4430 continue;
4431 cd = &m3d_commandtypes[cmd->type];
4432 *out++ = (cmd->type & 0x7F) | (cmd->type > 127 ? 0x80 : 0);
4433 if (cmd->type > 127) *out++ = (cmd->type >> 7) & 0xff;
4434 for (k = n = 0, l = cd->p; k < l; k++) {
4435 switch (cd->a[((k - n) % (cd->p - n)) + n]) {
4436 case m3dcp_mi_t:
4437 out = _m3d_addidx(out, si_s, cmd->arg[k] < model->nummaterial ? _m3d_stridx(str, numstr, model->material[cmd->arg[k]].name) : 0);
4438 break;
4439 case m3dcp_vc_t:
4440 min_x = *((float *)&cmd->arg[k]);
4441 switch (vc_s) {
4442 case 1: *out++ = (int8_t)(min_x * 127); break;
4443 case 2:
4444 *((int16_t *)out) = (int16_t)(min_x * 32767);
4445 out += 2;
4446 break;
4447 case 4:
4448 *((float *)out) = min_x;
4449 out += 4;
4450 break;
4451 case 8:
4452 *((double *)out) = min_x;
4453 out += 8;
4454 break;
4455 }
4456 break;
4457 case m3dcp_hi_t: out = _m3d_addidx(out, hi_s, cmd->arg[k]); break;
4458 case m3dcp_fi_t: out = _m3d_addidx(out, fi_s, cmd->arg[k]); break;
4459 case m3dcp_ti_t: out = _m3d_addidx(out, ti_s, cmd->arg[k]); break;
4460 case m3dcp_qi_t:
4461 case m3dcp_vi_t: out = _m3d_addidx(out, vi_s, cmd->arg[k]); break;
4462 case m3dcp_i1_t: out = _m3d_addidx(out, 1, cmd->arg[k]); break;
4463 case m3dcp_i2_t: out = _m3d_addidx(out, 2, cmd->arg[k]); break;
4464 case m3dcp_i4_t: out = _m3d_addidx(out, 4, cmd->arg[k]); break;
4465 case m3dcp_va_t:
4466 out = _m3d_addidx(out, 4, cmd->arg[k]);
4467 n = k + 1;
4468 l += (cmd->arg[k] - 1) * (cd->p - k - 1);
4469 break;
4470 }
4471 }
4472 }
4473 uint32_t v = (uint32_t)((uintptr_t)out - (uintptr_t)((uint8_t *)h + len));
4474 memcpy( length, &v, sizeof(uint32_t));
4475 len += v;
4476 out = NULL;
4477 }
4478 }
4479 /* annotation labels */
4480 if (model->numlabel && model->label) {
4481 for (i = 0, length = NULL; i < model->numlabel; i++) {
4482 if (!i || _m3d_strcmp(sl, model->label[i].lang) || _m3d_strcmp(sn, model->label[i].name)) {
4483 sl = model->label[i].lang;
4484 sn = model->label[i].name;
4485 if (length) {
4486 *length = (uint32_t)((uintptr_t)out - (uintptr_t)((uint8_t *)h + len));
4487 len += *length;
4488 }
4489 chunklen = 8 + 2 * si_s + ci_s + model->numlabel * (vi_s + si_s);
4490 h = (m3dhdr_t *)M3D_REALLOC(h, len + chunklen);
4491 if (!h) {
4492 sn = NULL;
4493 sl = NULL;
4494 goto memerr;
4495 }
4496 memcpy((uint8_t *)h + len, "LBLS", 4);
4497 length = (uint32_t *)((uint8_t *)h + len + 4);
4498 out = (uint8_t *)h + len + 8;
4499 out = _m3d_addidx(out, si_s, _m3d_stridx(str, numstr, model->label[l].name));
4500 out = _m3d_addidx(out, si_s, _m3d_stridx(str, numstr, model->label[l].lang));
4501 idx = _m3d_cmapidx(cmap, numcmap, model->label[i].color);
4502 switch (ci_s) {
4503 case 1: *out++ = (uint8_t)(idx); break;
4504 case 2:
4505 *((uint16_t *)out) = (uint16_t)(idx);
4506 out += 2;
4507 break;
4508 case 4:
4509 *((uint32_t *)out) = model->label[i].color;
4510 out += 4;
4511 break;
4512 }
4513 }
4514 out = _m3d_addidx(out, vi_s, vrtxidx[model->label[i].vertexid]);
4515 out = _m3d_addidx(out, si_s, _m3d_stridx(str, numstr, model->label[l].text));
4516 }
4517 if (length) {
4518 uint32_t v = (uint32_t)((uintptr_t)out - (uintptr_t)((uint8_t *)h + len));
4519 memcpy( length, &v, sizeof(uint32_t));
4520 len += v;
4521 }
4522 out = NULL;
4523 sn = sl = NULL;
4524 }
4525 /* actions */
4526 if (model->numaction && model->action && model->numbone && model->bone && !(flags & M3D_EXP_NOACTION)) {
4527 for (j = 0; j < model->numaction; j++) {
4528 a = &model->action[j];
4529 chunklen = 14 + si_s + a->numframe * (4 + fc_s + maxt * (bi_s + 2 * vi_s));
4530 h = (m3dhdr_t *)M3D_REALLOC(h, len + chunklen);
4531 if (!h) goto memerr;
4532 memcpy((uint8_t *)h + len, "ACTN", 4);
4533 length = (uint32_t *)((uint8_t *)h + len + 4);
4534 out = (uint8_t *)h + len + 8;
4535 out = _m3d_addidx(out, si_s, _m3d_stridx(str, numstr, a->name));
4536 *((uint16_t *)out) = (uint16_t)(a->numframe);
4537 out += 2;
4538 *((uint32_t *)out) = (uint32_t)(a->durationmsec);
4539 out += 4;
4540 for (i = 0; i < a->numframe; i++) {
4541 *((uint32_t *)out) = (uint32_t)(a->frame[i].msec);
4542 out += 4;
4543 out = _m3d_addidx(out, fc_s, a->frame[i].numtransform);
4544 for (k = 0; k < a->frame[i].numtransform; k++) {
4545 out = _m3d_addidx(out, bi_s, a->frame[i].transform[k].boneid);
4546 out = _m3d_addidx(out, vi_s, vrtxidx[a->frame[i].transform[k].pos]);
4547 out = _m3d_addidx(out, vi_s, vrtxidx[a->frame[i].transform[k].ori]);
4548 }
4549 }
4550 uint32_t v = (uint32_t)((uintptr_t)out - (uintptr_t)((uint8_t *)h + len));
4551 memcpy( length, &v, sizeof(uint32_t));
4552 len += v;
4553 out = NULL;
4554 }
4555 }
4556 /* inlined assets */
4557 if (model->numinlined && model->inlined && (numproc || (flags & M3D_EXP_INLINE))) {
4558 for (j = 0; j < model->numinlined; j++) {
4559 if (!model->inlined[j].name || !model->inlined[j].name[0] || model->inlined[j].length < 4 || !model->inlined[j].data)
4560 continue;
4561 if (!(flags & M3D_EXP_INLINE)) {
4562 if (model->inlined[j].data[1] == 'P' && model->inlined[j].data[2] == 'N' && model->inlined[j].data[3] == 'G')
4563 continue;
4564 for (i = k = 0; i < model->numtexture; i++) {
4565 if (!strcmp(model->inlined[j].name, model->texture[i].name)) {
4566 k = 1;
4567 break;
4568 }
4569 }
4570 if (k) continue;
4571 }
4572 chunklen = 8 + si_s + model->inlined[j].length;
4573 h = (m3dhdr_t *)M3D_REALLOC(h, len + chunklen);
4574 if (!h) goto memerr;
4575 memcpy((uint8_t *)h + len, "ASET", 4);
4576 *((uint32_t *)((uint8_t *)h + len + 4)) = chunklen;
4577 out = (uint8_t *)h + len + 8;
4578 out = _m3d_addidx(out, si_s, _m3d_stridx(str, numstr, model->inlined[j].name));
4579 memcpy(out, model->inlined[j].data, model->inlined[j].length);
4580 out = NULL;
4581 len += chunklen;
4582 }
4583 }
4584 /* extra chunks */
4585 if (model->numextra && model->extra && (flags & M3D_EXP_EXTRA)) {
4586 for (j = 0; j < model->numextra; j++) {
4587 if (!model->extra[j] || model->extra[j]->length < 8)
4588 continue;
4589 chunklen = model->extra[j]->length;
4590 h = (m3dhdr_t *)M3D_REALLOC(h, len + chunklen);
4591 if (!h) goto memerr;
4592 memcpy((uint8_t *)h + len, model->extra[j], chunklen);
4593 len += chunklen;
4594 }
4595 }
4596 /* add end chunk */
4597 h = (m3dhdr_t *)M3D_REALLOC(h, len + 4);
4598 if (!h) goto memerr;
4599 memcpy((uint8_t *)h + len, "OMD3", 4);
4600 len += 4;
4601 /* zlib compress */
4602 if (!(flags & M3D_EXP_NOZLIB)) {
4603 M3D_LOG("Deflating chunks");
4604 z = stbi_zlib_compress((unsigned char *)h, len, (int *)&l, 9);
4605 if (z && l > 0 && l < len) {
4606 len = l;
4607 M3D_FREE(h);
4608 h = (m3dhdr_t *)z;
4609 }
4610 }
4611 /* add file header at the beginning */
4612 len += 8;
4613 out = (unsigned char *)M3D_MALLOC(len);
4614 if (!out) goto memerr;
4615 memcpy(out, "3DMO", 4);
4616 *((uint32_t *)(out + 4)) = len;
4617 memcpy(out + 8, h, len - 8);
4618 }
4619 if (size) *size = out ? len : 0;
4620 if (vrtxidx) M3D_FREE(vrtxidx);
4621 if (mtrlidx) M3D_FREE(mtrlidx);
4622 if (tmapidx) M3D_FREE(tmapidx);
4623 if (skinidx) M3D_FREE(skinidx);
4624 if (norm) M3D_FREE(norm);
4625 if (face) M3D_FREE(face);
4626 if (cmap) M3D_FREE(cmap);
4627 if (tmap) M3D_FREE(tmap);
4628 if (skin) M3D_FREE(skin);
4629 if (str) M3D_FREE(str);
4630 if (vrtx) M3D_FREE(vrtx);
4631 if (h) M3D_FREE(h);
4632 return out;
4633}
4634#endif
4635
4636#endif /* M3D_IMPLEMENTATION */
